{"tid":326033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃其他地區附加賽名額賽四強","createTime":"2017-07-17T15:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T14:08:23.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"304ce8e1a1f31cea5ffb072c1946982777958181","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n12:00am Nina Dobrev(加拿大) vs 李海娜(泰國)<br />\n12:02am Shakira(哥倫比亞) vs 林詩枝(馬來西亞)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nP.S 如LIHKG App版本過舊,有可能無法使用回覆評分功能<br />\n請先更新或改以Web版LIHKG投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ad2bd7d9e44e7373dfd2039232d4d5366a8827","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃其他地區附加賽名額賽四強</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-18 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qJjTal0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqJjTal0.png&h=15b689c6&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/T6mGxcL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FT6mGxcL.png&h=c04ef065&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KADRdM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKADRdM3.png&h=6f0730a8&s={SIZE}\" />Nina Dobrev vs 李海娜<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qdKYOI7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqdKYOI7.png&h=8719e985&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"3b6ccfff6695eab146a0f3eb23e45ffd245ee2e2","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-18 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/t3t8Ubj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ft3t8Ubj.png&h=7eafbd04&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nNFpF39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnNFpF39.png&h=d1728cc3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UNwV3ax.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUNwV3ax.png&h=7dca293a&s={SIZE}\" />Shakira vs 林詩枝<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/i2eVNeb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi2eVNeb.png&h=8fa43878&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"a7873fd4f5c074a72945971892bb7a16ad380ba1","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:02:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又係呼籲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實投票，唔一定每種投票既性質都係要大家識或者鍾意果一個人先至可以投票<br />\n大家可以憑住審美眼光黎投票，決定邊個好啲靚啲咪投邊個，選美評審都唔會知道面前既女仔係咩人，只係客觀選擇<br />\n巴打們不妨可以抱住呢個心態黎參與我地既活動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8ebb88ce682320a77c67979f1337ba7c8575bf","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685e24a5ced5186529b7aff4a93da599c1b3ce60","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b69248f3a5eb30150ea368f9685a8f9e4107e9","tid":326033,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:24:29.000Z","msg":"2負評"},{"pid":"dbb03e1076411eb3b426168d7d13a9e27fe46df6","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2負評</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a202bc8a05d3de7f58d26746b6e77ba29f37875","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2e16b013d63b13ce140b87833e95703027