/>\n關d「女神」事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4個都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28480b3a0af2621e80a9f923f626c3feb1f5e4c8","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分到勝負,都OK...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">點解會仲差過回覆投票年代</span></span></blockquote><br />\n關d「女神」事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4個都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識就唔投得,呢種觀念一時三刻真係好難改,但我會繼續呼籲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到個比賽咁大,但會員眼界唔肯擴闊,唔識就無辦法選擇<br />\n其實真係大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撳個掣啫,叫你娶左佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a711f78df917bbdcc99f5de5d5922077e33930","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc12124aac1cf02cfc578220a3116739661c4f46","tid":326033,"uid":114678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T22:23:32.000Z","msg":"票已投"},{"pid":"8eb2f1249a653e83d8d6c87134db09273b3f67e3","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>票已投</blockquote><br />\n多謝你踴躍投票參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c106119a75acd097c3272c0fb7472fa9096ea09b","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d70516ad39c07685ee0453be4cfe8770b1b30c7","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72369aa7e42ecf3fe2b9fb29694835c759d2cd95","tid":326033,"uid":78630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"無左賽事評述無咁過癮"},{"pid":"892f0544fdefb6283cc9d45c04c2b33fa6b21d85","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無左賽事評述無咁過癮</blockquote><br />\n可以加返既,不過都無乜人投,有旁述都唔知講到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8c9018a85331779cb5c39766f2591a09947690","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaf73bc3d3ee106411217c4d79499f2c5cc24da","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3253fcd26b2b6c6ed7af66700dc39cf1697beb5","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7374a2ffd6f9a687c1001d5bc7d692dc959ec1a","tid":326033,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b4345a120ee392ef5113afd7b2c973a90c1a5d","tid":326033,"uid":